  "body": "Friday, August 12 at 14:00 UTC (10:00 ET)\r\nDuration: 60 mins\r\n\r\n‚Üí [Zoom Link](https://ethereumfoundation.zoom.us/j/88654262834?pwd=K1VtcElFU0hKL2szQXF4RmF4VVA4Zz09)\r\n‚Üí [Add to your calendar](https://calendar.google.com/event?action=TEMPLATE&tmeid=MDhqbDRiZXJtbmZlZWpzb2U0aDhzcWkzbmogY191cGFvZm9uZzhtZ3JtcmtlZ243aWM3aGs1c0Bn&tmsrc=c_upaofong8mgrmrkegn7ic7hk5s%40group.calendar.google.com)\r\n‚Üí [Subscribe](https://calendar.google.com/calendar/u/1?cid=Y191cGFvZm9uZzhtZ3JtcmtlZ243aWM3aGs1c0Bncm91cC5jYWxlbmRhci5nb29nbGUuY29t) to the Ethereum Protocol Call calendar\r\n\r\n## Pre-call Resources\r\n- [How The Merge Impacts Ethereum‚Äôs Application Layer](https://blog.ethereum.org/2021/11/29/how-the-merge-impacts-app-layer/)\r\n- [AllCoreDevs Update 007 ‚õì](https://hackmd.io/@timbeiko/acd/https%3A%2F%2Ftim.mirror.xyz%2FsR23jU02we6zXRgsF_oTUkttL83S3vyn05vJWnnp-Lc) - details about post merge Execution and Consensus client architectures\r\n- [Mega Merge Resource List üêº](https://notes.ethereum.org/Moiv99h9QTmI-imPL8pvQg?view)\r\n\r\n## Discussion\r\n- Goerli updates\r\n- CL client balance (prysm to lighthouse)\r\n- [post-Merge testnets](https://ethereum-magicians.org/t/og-council-post-merge-testnets/9034)\r\n- block times go from ~13s to exactly 12s. may impact lending protocols and how they calculate annual rates (use timestamps)\r\n- setting fee recipient: tx fees go to validator address on the Execution layer: [see here](https://github.com/ethereum/execution-apis/blob/main/src/engine/specification.md#payloadattributesv1)\r\n- Validators need to run both Execution and Consensus clients - and diversity matters for both EL and CL clients: [guides here](https://clientdiversity.org/#switch)\r\n\r\n‚Üì Leave a comment to add a topic ‚Üì",
